      "text": "  %spark_high.pyspark\r\n\r\n  # 실제 INSERT 라인 샘플 확인\r\n  sample_lines \u003d table_rdd.take(3)\r\n  for i, l in enumerate(sample_lines):\r\n      print(f\"--- 라인 {i+1} (앞 300자) ---\")\r\n      print(repr(l[:300]))\r\n      print()\r\n\r\n  # parse_insert_line 직접 테스트\r\n  if sample_lines:\r\n      result \u003d parse_insert_line(sample_lines[0])\r\n      print(f\"파싱 결과: {result}\")",
